Class PaAttributeValueErrorInformationUnsupportedVersionBuilderIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute.util.PaAttributeValueErrorInformationUnsupportedVersionBuilderIetf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class PaAttributeValueErrorInformationUnsupportedVersionBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PaAttributeValueErrorInformationUnsupportedVersionBuilder
    Builder to build an integrity measurement unsupported version error information value compliant to RFC 5792. It can be used in a fluent way.
